<issue
   id="RBN-3"
   type="mapping_table"
   linkend="ae entity=Envelope_association aa attribute=related assertion_to=Envelope"
   status="open"
   category="editorial"
   by="Rob Bodington"
   date="03-01-24">
<description>
The mapping refpath should always start with the AIM entity to which the ARM
entity has been mapped. It should also end with the AIM entity to which the
assertion has been mapped.
  <screen>
    envelope_relationship &lt;=
    product_relationship
    product_relationship.related_product -&gt;
    product &lt;-
    product_related_product_category.products[i]
    product_related_product_category &lt;=
    product_category
    product_category.name='envelope' 
  </screen>
</description>
</issue>


